Subject: [PATCH 1/3] Add app rule hotkeys and dev app packaging

- Add per-app activation hotkeys and actions for open, rotate, and pull-right
- Add workspace-to-next-monitor movement and preserve bindings on import
- Add scripts and Makefile targets for building and installing the dev app
